{"tid":680522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西貢黑幫血案　警一度拔槍","createTime":"2018-05-27T08:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T04:46:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9122e8908f47095303071f83c2717c5a88ff5123","tid":680522,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:59:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180527/20402751\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180527%2F20402751&d=GXNzoZh0xSHPFw8hkR3%2Bf4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=0b327536\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180527%2F20402751&h=5aa80a8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180527/20402751</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月27日 <br />\n<br />\n西貢黑幫血案　警一度拔槍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180527/large/27la5p05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180527%2Flarge%2F27la5p05.jpg&h=33ff73a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大前晚西貢黑幫斬人血案，反遭圍毆的刀手被打至血流披面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】大前晚西貢黑幫和勝和惡鬥水房斬人血案，警方東九龍總區反黑組接手調查後，前日再拘捕七人，案件至今共拘捕十男一女（21至50歲），分別有和勝和及水房背景，而當晚警員為制止雙方械鬥，在發出口頭警告不果後一度拔槍戒備。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再拘六男一女<br />\n<br />\n案中被追斬水房26歲小頭目姓黃男子及四名刀手受傷，事後要送院治療。消息稱，此宗斬人血案緣於一筆約400萬元街數，活躍深水埗及西九龍的勝和小頭目「肥仔亮」經營一間財務公司，近期指水房姓黃叫Ken的小頭目與一筆400萬元巨債有關，多次追討無果，有人查悉Ken大前晚會在西貢翠塘路一間海鮮酒家出現，於是部署刀手乘車向他施下馬再追數。<br />\n<br />\n豈料對方當時原來剛出席完「大佬」壽宴，阿Ken遇襲後約30多名同門反擊，將刀手包圍追打，其中四刀手被打至血流披面，其後警員到場拔槍戒備始控制場面，當場拘捕四名受傷刀手。東九龍總區反黑組接手，前日再拘捕六男一女，包括涉案車輛車主。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃祺文  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n子涉鼠藥混湯圖殺母<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n中大澳門男生　宿舍上吊亡"},{"pid":"d7431fb3f23888bb9052f147adc9a3927023cdc3","tid":680522,"uid":71433,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:15:02.000Z","msg":"食物大戰 生菜斬排骨"},{"pid":"7640fd9056dae0f6c720e41b44068090c058f8e3","tid":680522,"uid":11301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:24:39.000Z","msg":"油麻they"},{"pid":"0aa478f3ff4353fe23e609099b3116b623158f9d","tid":680522,"uid":39698,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/173049_c548cbe7a1a352c7e20f719b5a567c4a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F173049_c548cbe7a1a352c7e20f719b5a567c4a.png&h=43c9aded&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d74d5f85fabd2e8fc98fd3ce3a896e446656fc4","tid":680522,"uid":83927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:36:57.000Z","msg":"揸刀對拳頭都輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e88380766276eac99f4b983890c24470876d989","tid":680522,"uid":22839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:40:55.000Z","msg":"借錢比對面啲人<br />\n啲黑社會係咪豬閪嚟"},{"pid":"95270a463d15a12334d30e050f3cdca6deffb0fb","tid":680522,"uid":102096,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:54:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2bb677ccfb93e9f581ec82442cfa6b859db2e74","tid":680522,"uid":49247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d74d5f85fabd2e8fc98fd3ce3a896e446656fc4","tid":680522,"uid":83927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:36:57.000Z","msg":"揸刀對拳頭都輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:58:32.000Z","msg":"一人夾一隻手都收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062b498fdd4115895586a303b019d49e1fdb46d4",